issue.title: [CF 711] UnitAura in 5.1
issue.body:
I saw this mentioned elsewhere, but it appears UnitAura now returns an additional value between isBossDebuff and value1. This ends up breaking the [Stacks] DogTag on the icons and maybe other things. Adding an extra "_," before all the value1 entries appears to fix it.


> Posted by CurseForge user amoeba3 | Imported from CurseForge issue #711 | Raw
